<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَقْتُ الظُّهْر<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{أَقِمِ الصَّلَاةَ لِدُلُوكِ الشَّمْسِ إِلَى غَسَقِ اللَّيْلِ وَقُرْآَنَ الْفَجْرِ إِنَّ قُرْآَنَ الْفَجْرِ كَانَ مَشْهُودًا}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [الإسراء/٧٨]</p> </div>